    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在冷战高峰期执行一项高风险的间谍行动。拦截并破译加密通信，揭示隐藏的威胁。破解密码，通过社会工程操控目标，串联线索，在为时已晚之前逃脱。<strong> <br><br>From Basement with Love</strong> 是一款结合了逻辑谜题、侦探调查和视觉小说元素的2D冒险游戏。    <br> <br>作为冷战时期的一名卧底间谍，你被指派执行一项危险任务，揭露威胁全球安全的秘密军事行动。 <br> <br> <br>一个小小的地下室既是你的生活空间，也是你秘密行动的指挥中心。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339280/extras/fe00c15ad29d2d5ba18e8728f5cd29eb.poster.avif?t=1771589454\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339280/extras/fe00c15ad29d2d5ba18e8728f5cd29eb.webm?t=1771589454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339280/extras/fe00c15ad29d2d5ba18e8728f5cd29eb.mp4?t=1771589454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br>你的书桌配备了可以拦截并破译加密通信的设备。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339280/extras/86bee208283ef1403d6f6483094fda10.poster.avif?t=1771589454\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339280/extras/86bee208283ef1403d6f6483094fda10.webm?t=1771589454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339280/extras/86bee208283ef1403d6f6483094fda10.mp4?t=1771589454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >时刻保持警惕，追踪并拦截传输的信息。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339280/extras/81cc73acf2fc7763e94c3e8fa639b018.poster.avif?t=1771589454\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339280/extras/81cc73acf2fc7763e94c3e8fa639b018.webm?t=1771589454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339280/extras/81cc73acf2fc7763e94c3e8fa639b018.mp4?t=1771589454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用合适的设备破译加密通信，发现即将到来的威胁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339280/extras/7dc65d790d97b925aac3ba31ea789493.poster.avif?t=1771589454\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339280/extras/7dc65d790d97b925aac3ba31ea789493.webm?t=1771589454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339280/extras/7dc65d790d97b925aac3ba31ea789493.mp4?t=1771589454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过社会工程操控目标人物，获取更多信息，揭开全部真相。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339280/extras/0166ac226232b173f3b3a1f3a63b3177.poster.avif?t=1771589454\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339280/extras/0166ac226232b173f3b3a1f3a63b3177.webm?t=1771589454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339280/extras/0166ac226232b173f3b3a1f3a63b3177.mp4?t=1771589454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
